{"word":"H4980 - מַתָּנָה - Mattânâh - mat-taw-naw' - Mattanah","slug":"H4980","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַתָּנָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Mattânâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mat-taw-naw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Mattanah"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>מתּנה</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>mattânâh</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>mat-taw-naw'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Mattanah = \"gift of Jehovah\" <ol><li>a station of the Israelites in the latter part of their wanderings located east of the Jordan and probably to the southeast of the Dead Sea</li></ol> <p />Origin: the same as <a href=\"#/H4979\">H4979</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4976\">H4976</a>, <a href=\"#/H4977\">H4977</a>, <a href=\"#/H4979\">H4979</a>, <a href=\"#/H4982\">H4982</a>, <a href=\"#/H4983\">H4983</a>, <a href=\"#/H4991\">H4991</a>, <a href=\"#/H4992\">H4992</a>, <a href=\"#/H4993\">H4993</a>, <a href=\"#/H5411\">H5411</a>, <a href=\"#/H5414\">H5414</a>, <a href=\"#/H5416\">H5416</a>, <a href=\"#/H5417\">H5417</a>, <a href=\"#/H5418\">H5418</a>, <a href=\"#/H5419\">H5419</a>"}]}